<%- include('./partials/header.ejs') %>

<body>
  <%- include('./partials/homenavbar.ejs') %>
  <div class="container mb-2 mt-2">
    <%- include('./partials/categories.ejs') %>
  </div>
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="jumbotron p-3 p-md-5 text-dark rounded">
      <div class="col-md-6 px-0 mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="display-4 font-italic">Blog do WeneDev</h1>
        <p class="lead my-3 text-justify">Lorem, ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Optio velit eum aut
          odio necessitatibus cumque ex repudiandae, ullam distinctio eveniet enim iusto, officia labore adipisci ipsa
          corrupti laudantium explicabo provident.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container mb-2 mt-2">
    <h3 class="pb-3 mb-4 font-italic border-bottom">
      Posts recentes!
    </h3>
    <div class="row mb-1">
      <% if(articles.length > 0){%>
      <% articles.forEach(article =>{%>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card flex-md-row mb-4 shadow-sm h-md-250">
          <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column align-items-start">
            <strong class="d-inline-block mb-2 text-primary"><%= article.category.title %></strong>
            <h4 class="mb-0">
              <a class="text-dark" href="/<%= article.slug %>"><%= article.title %></a>
            </h4>
            <div class="mb-1 text-muted"><%= new Date(article.updatedAt).toLocaleDateString() %> às
              <%= new Date(article.updatedAt).toLocaleTimeString() %></div>
            <p class="card-text mb-auto"><%= article.sinopse %></p>
            <a href="/<%= article.slug %>" class="btn-link mt-1">Continue lendo</a>
          </div>
          <img class="card-img-right flex-auto d-none d-lg-block" data-src="holder.js/200x250?theme=thumb"
            alt="Card image cap" src="images/violino.jpg" width="200" height="250">
        </div>
      </div>
      <% }) %>
      <% }else{%>
      <div class="col-12 px-4 mx-auto text-center mb-5">
        <h1 class="display-4 font-italic m-3">Nenhum post foi encontrado!</h1>
      </div>
      <% } %>
    </div>
    <% if(articles.length > 0){%>
    <nav class="blog-pagination d-flex justify-content-end">
      <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary disabled" href="/">Mais novos</a>
      <a class="btn btn-outline-primary ml-2" href="/articles/page/2">Mais antigos</a>
    </nav>
    <% }else{%>
    <nav class="blog-pagination d-flex justify-content-end">
      <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary disabled" href="/">Mais novos</a>
      <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary disabled ml-2" href="/articles/page/2">Mais antigos</a>
    </nav>
    <% } %>
    <h3 class="pb-3 mb-4 font-italic border-bottom text-center" id="sobre">
      Sobre nós
    </h3>
    <div class="jumbotron">
      <div class="container">
        <h5 class="display-4">Olá, sou Wene Alves!</h5>
        <p>Trabalho com desenvolvimento web, atualmente estundando novas tecnologias para minha Stack, gosto muito da área de tecnologia, já praticipei de projetos da minha escola com a criação de uma game para deficientes auditivos,
        tô estundando NodeJs , React Native e dart flutter.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="https://github.com/wenealves10" target="_blank" role="button">Saiba mais &raquo;</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h3 class="pb-3 mb-4 font-italic border-bottom text-center" id="contato">
      Contato
    </h3>
  </div>
  <%- include('./partials/homefooter.ejs') %>
</body>
<%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>